metadata.name: THE CALLING INTO THE ABYSS - BRITANIA
metadata.description:
PAY HEED TO THE CALLING. 

INTO THE ABYSS.

OBEY THE THUNDEROUS THUMPS.

"t'was a sleepless night, 
I pictured the aliens hell bent on ending us. 
with each thump/cycle, 
signifies our journey towards the end of all"

I wanted to capture the emotions of fear in beauty & symmetry, both in audio and visual experience.


Full Lore & Description here : 
[THE CALLING](https://azlansyarawi.wixsite.com/home/thecalling)
soundtrack by SYARAWI |
